    "title": "SOC 2 for Japanese SaaS Companies: Compliance Guide for APAC Markets",
    "description": "Complete SOC 2 compliance guide for Japanese SaaS companies. Covers SOC 2 alignment with Japan's Act on Protection of Personal Information, ISMAP cloud security requirements, Financial Services Agency guidelines, and Japanese market auditor expectations.",
    "published": "2027-01-31",
