    "html": "<div class=\"answer-capsule\"><p>Spire and Sprinto offer SOC 2 automation with different geographic strengths and technical approaches in 2026 — Sprinto has strong adoption in India and APAC markets with automated evidence collection and a GRC-integrated platform, while Spire offers AI-native compliance with automated evidence evaluation and a global focus. Both platforms enable SOC 2 readiness in 6 to 12 weeks for most B2B SaaS companies.</p></div>\n<h2>Geographic Coverage and Market Focus</h2>\n<p>Sprinto has particularly strong adoption among Indian SaaS companies and APAC-based startups, with specific support for local compliance frameworks. Spire serves a global customer base with support for US, EU, and APAC compliance requirements. Both platforms support SOC 2, ISO 27001, HIPAA, GDPR, and PCI DSS compliance.</p>\n<h2>AI and Automation</h2>\n<p>Spire differentiates with its AI audit agent that automatically evaluates evidence and produces structured readiness reports. Sprinto provides automated evidence collection and policy management but without AI-powered evidence evaluation. Spire also offers AI-driven questionnaire response automation.</p>\n<h2>Pricing</h2>\n<p>Sprinto pricing starts at approximately $6,000 to $12,000 per year for SOC 2 coverage, positioning it as a cost-effective option for early-stage startups. Spire pricing is competitive with similar platform tiers. Both platforms offer multi-framework support.</p>\n<h2>Best-Fit Customer Profile</h2>\n<p>Spire is best for: global SaaS companies wanting AI-powered compliance automation, teams that want automated evidence evaluation, and companies handling high volumes of enterprise security questionnaires. Sprinto is best for: APAC-based SaaS companies, Indian startups seeking cost-effective compliance, and companies wanting a simple platform with essential automation.</p>\n<h2>FAQ</h2>\n<h3>Which platform has better ISO 27001 support?</h3>\n<p>Both platforms support ISO 27001 alongside SOC 2. Spire's AI audit agent provides specific value for ISO 27001 ISMS documentation review. Sprinto offers good ISO 27001 coverage for APAC-based companies.</p>\n<h3>Can either platform handle multi-entity compliance?</h3>\n<p>Spire supports multi-entity and multi-framework compliance for companies with multiple products or subsidiaries. Sprinto offers multi-framework support with a focus on SOC 2 and ISO 27001.</p>\n<h3>Which platform is better for US enterprise sales?</h3>\n<p>For US enterprise sales, SOC 2 Type II coverage is the primary requirement. Both platforms provide SOC 2 support. Spire's AI questionnaire response automation provides additional value for US enterprise sales cycles that involve extensive security reviews.</p>\n"
